      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly with no major leaks, and the transmission shifts reliably through all gears. While there are some minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major features are fully functional. It\u2019s a dependable car that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs required.",
