    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This model has been curated for the professional who demands both mechanical excellence and aesthetic poise. It exhibits a consistent maintenance history and a refined interior environment, ensuring a superior driving experience. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that perfectly balances performance with enduring value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
